Text: Bauer College of BusinessFriend We invite you to read the first newsletter issued by the CT BAUER COLLEGE OF BUSINESS In this newsletter we feature the onceinalifetime investment of million made by Mr Ted Bauer Chairman and CoFounder of AIM Management Group in the College that now bears his name Please take the time to read about the greatest event in the history of the College of Business In addition to Mr Bauers gift this newsletter also features information on a unique initiative between the Bauer College of Business and AIM Management Group and our features on key Bauer College programs faculty and staff You can find the newsletter at cbanewsletterFallindexhtm Jerry Jerry R Strawser Interim Dean Arthur Andersen Co Alumni Professor CT Bauer College of Business University of Houston Phone Fax wwwcbauhedujerry
